 the rule of law and confront the Trump administration’s illegal abductio
 ns\, detentions\, and deportations of people like Kilmar Abrego Garcia\, R
 ui Marras\, and Juan Maldonado Zuniga. 🚨 On the 1st Wednesday of the mo
 nth\, we’re showing up in West Sacramento at the corner of Jefferson Blv
 d. and Park
